title: The Nicolas Cage Hall of Fame and ‘The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent’
description:
It’s Nic Cage season! To celebrate, Van Lathan and Rob Mahoney join Sean to talk about the new meta-action-comedy ‘The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent’ (1:00) before building a shrine to Cage in the form of his Hall of Fame (35:00).

Hosts: Sean Fennessey
Guests: Van Lathan and Rob Mahoney
Producer: Bobby Wagner
